oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: A soldier on leave
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: An unidentified man is standing in a small boat in a bathing suit, holding a pole. Two women can be seen behind him in the water. There is a hat hanging in the foreground on the right.
